data.eml:eml: SPC PROCFish/C Invertebrates Observations Solomon Islands 2006

Marine invertebrate species of commercial interest observed in Solomon Islands during the PROCFish/C surveys (2006) in 4 sites Nggela, Chubikopi, Marau and Rarumana with a mix of survey methods (manta tow, reef benthos transects, and day and night searches)
